{"tid":414882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［荃灣人］大河道呃錢黨","createTime":"2017-09-26T14:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T16:04:12.000Z","uid":54724,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd702c9a9259e21eb2e259b70a94ec0a51299cc","tid":414882,"uid":54724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"只不過等馬路幾秒鐘<br />\n係我後面叫我捐錢  <br />\n咁我一個微笑拒絕 但其實拎緊個錢包出嚟 個阿婆即刻鬧唔切 （咁後生都唔捐錢 無用呀你&hellip;。）<br />\n即係咁<br />\n呢個［<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">長者享樂慈善社</span></strong>］搵埋啲毒舌癈老 心地咁差 就咪學人<del>行乞</del>募捐啦<br />\n<br />\n之前已經有同學提醒過我 <br />\n叫我咪捐比D阿婆 不過手快捐左 <br />\n嗰時個阿婆已經出口成文 讚到我天上有 地下無 不過你踩親我條尾 咁啱又走咗架車 畀晒機會我 咁我就影你出嚟la<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/26/215849_342a5d2e2e7c8230c677f9f94a8c35ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2F215849_342a5d2e2e7c8230c677f9f94a8c35ee.jpg&h=86234ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇吓阿婆個樣 究竟係收緊數定募捐緊<br />\n<br />\nD好人比你地殺死晒啦 <span style=\"color: blue;\">無福</span>享樂慈善社"},{"pid":"6aca62cb1c1ee9a24ce7ca6653701d03add3eec3","tid":414882,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"下次買定d陰司紙，塞滿個箱<br />\n屌鳩返佢地，你地個頭近，捐定俾你地班<br />\n廢老落到地府用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2966afb4a1d60abbda47fd330c91d82a9d72bfa","tid":414882,"uid":68414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"次次經過都比啲啊婆叫我做善事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4de7810508fd3228ef92197fef32199c971d6ce","tid":414882,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"中環都好恐怖<br />\nlandmark 附近成隊足球隊咁係d 班馬線開工<br />\n<br />\n仲有ifc 天橋個旅行冇錢返屋企鬼佬<br />\n日日都開工<br />\n有時好想去佢面前讚佢 you are so hardworking"},{"pid":"c9aad5397928a5f578048600f07ad4fe3103fc42","tid":414882,"uid":35774,"like":0,"disl